3 (b) Transfer prohibitions.
4 (1) On and after July 1, 2025, the Commissioner shall neither negotiate
5 nor execute contracts for the assignment or transfer of individuals to an out-of-
6 state correctional facility unless the facility is operated by a public or nonprofit
7 entity to house individuals pursuant to an interstate compact or federal
8 contract.
9 (2) On and after January 1, 2030, the Commissioner shall terminate or
10 amend any existing contracts to be compliant with this section.
